rần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%C3%A2n-M%C3%B9i-th%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-ERxN6rsYIVq6ZYNznX5QwA">Tân Mùi thất tịch - 辛未七夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-h%E1%BB%AFu-v%C3%A3n-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-S73uSTGHZ97iGKokdkV5OQ">Tịnh hữu vãn thi kỳ 2 - 并有輓詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Giao/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-b%C3%A1ch-thi%E1%BB%87t/poem-PJimNiUJ0unD7IeKvACWtQ">Vịnh bách thiệt - 詠百舌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Giao/author-VVl3mnm6-DXAxMiEF4IPnw">Nguyễn Văn Giao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Xu%C3%A2n-hi%E1%BB%83u/poem-cZRx4GRlCqEeB8CMkMoCzQ">Xuân hiểu - 春曉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Qu%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn/Xu%C3%A2n-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi-hi%E1%BB%87u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Xuy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-b0lVaHG5wN40Hu-ickJ1_g">Xuân sầu thi hiệu Ngọc Xuyên tử - 春愁詩效玉川子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Qu%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn/author-HlAsEr3qGyMOUeGTRRdhhQ">Tiết Quý Tuyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
